        <img src="path_to_art_piece_image" alt="3D Printed Art Piece">
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Fun Facts</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Nike:</strong> Uses 3D printing to create prototypes of new shoes. They can test and tweak designs quickly.</li>
            <li><strong>DIY 3D Printers:</strong> Companies like RepRap sell kits so you can build your own 3D printer at home.</li>
            <li><strong>Food:</strong> Yes, you can even print food! Imagine a 3D-printed chocolate bar.</li>
        </ul>
